<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              xmlns:local="clr-namespace:RFEM_Software.Help_Files.RDam_Help_Files"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="14" FontFamily="Georgia">
    <Paragraph>
        Enabling this option will cause the first random log-conductivity field
(ie. the first realization) to be plotted as a DISPLAY format file having
extension *.fld. It can be post-processed by display.exe to produce a
PostScript plot which can then be view using Ghostview. This can be also
be accomplished using the Results menu item.
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>
